Good evening Colleen, thank you for sending over the estimate for the caliper and timing chain gasket replacement on Sylvie's 2017 Ram 3500. Please be advised, the customer is responsible for any diagnostic fees, shop supplies, environmental fees, and fluids + fluid exchanges (brake fluid flush), as well as a $100 deductible. Additionally, our Mitchell Labour Guide allows for 3.4 hours for the timing chain cover gasket replacement, and 0.9 hours for the caliper replacement. Our maximum payout for labour is $130/h. If you choose to charge an amount that is above this maximum labour payout, the customer will be responsible for the difference. The payout is as follows:

Parts-$278.88
Labour-$559.00 (4.3 hours x $130/h) 
Deductible-$100.00
Tax-$95.92
Authorization-ABDEHAIKMU

Total = $833.80

Once the repair is complete, please send us a copy of the final invoice for payment. 

Best regards, 


Matthew Puls
